## Development Environment

### Dev Container
- Open in VS Code → "Reopen in Container"
- Resources: 6 CPUs, 24GB RAM
- Tools: kubectl, helm, k3d, tilt{{ if hasItem .Project.Spec.Infrastructure.Components "hasura" }}, hasura{{ end }}{{ if .Project.Spec.GitOps.Enabled }}, argocd{{ end }}

### Local Kubernetes (k3d)
- Cluster: `k3d-{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}-cluster`
- Registry: `k3d-{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}-registry:5005`
- Namespace: `{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}`

### Tilt (Hot Reload)
- Start: `tilt up`
- Dashboard: http://localhost:10350
- Services auto-rebuild on file changes
{{ if .Computed.HasNode }}
### Hot Reload Rules (Node.js)
- Source changes (`src/`) → nodemon restarts process (~2s)
- Package changes (`packages/node/*/dist/`) → nodemon restarts dependent services
- `package.json` changes → container rebuild
- Only packages a service depends on are synced (selective package sync)
{{ end }}
### Helm Charts
- All services use the shared `_lib/service` library chart
- Service charts are in `k8s/helm/{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}/`
- Infrastructure charts are in `k8s/helm/infra/`
- Image registry: `{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}/SERVICE_NAME` (local k3d)
